neutron strength functions and level densities. A

.The neutron and radiation width were deduced with
simultaneous fit of both the capture and transmission
data up 80 keV neutron energy. The spin assignment
(g and J) and angular momentum (L) were taken from
ENDF/B-VI. The g factor was verified by fitting of
of the thick and thin sample transmission factors.
